snippet: Tiger Woods, who has not played the Honda Classic since he was 17 and an amateur, clashed with a reporter during a news conference Wednesday.
abstract: Tiger Woods, who has not played the Honda Classic since he was 17 and an amateur, clashes with a reporter during a news conference over a tell-all book by Woods's former coach Hank Haney.
lead_paragraph: Tiger Woods, who has not played the Honda Classic since he was 17 and an amateur, clashed with a reporter during a news conference Wednesday.

headline.seo: Tiger Woods at Honda Classic for First Time Since ’93
headline.main: In Return to the Honda Classic, Woods Is Irritated by Some Questioning
headline.print_headline: Woods Is Angered Over Book Questions
